{"tid":222691,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"LIHKG香港超級女神聯賽 季尾速報-- 莊錠欣、袁澧林篤定降班","createTime":"2017-04-29T17:12:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T13:48:40.000Z","uid":92376,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ac334c218c6e2f1e10d97f246531bc020f4e9bc7","tid":222691,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T17:12:34.000Z","msg":"4月30日凌晨香港消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n港超第14位莊錠欣(Elkie Chong)及第15位袁澧林(Angela Yuen)剛完成超聯第29輪賽事: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/221521\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/221521</a><br />\n莊錠欣29戰得25分,袁澧林29戰得24分<br />\n聯賽僅餘一輪下,兩人均無法超越位於安全線,第13位,29戰得29分既杜小喬<br />\n提早一輪宣佈降班,來季將會降落港冠女神聯賽<br />\n<br />\n降班:<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/dyvWvIn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdyvWvIn.png&h=905c20d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n莊錠欣（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Nr0V19R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNr0V19R.png&h=28b169dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n袁澧林（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n護級成功:<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/PQwdgr1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPQwdgr1.png&h=09784725&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n杜小喬（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n*第16位 岑晉晴已篤定降班,而且戰績極其差劣(29戰全敗),有可能直接移出整個聯賽,取消其參賽資格"},{"pid":"fb08383e533d5ffadadb6a55b0832136e0d1a268","tid":222691,"uid":1424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T17:15:03.000Z","msg":"哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4937353abb91bbbbe5d773c8b1070c730e14871f","tid":222691,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T17:16:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請尊重一眾參與巴打努力投票下得出既公正結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d8ce2b7d7189da65bbbce71dcab